sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant App as Webview
participant Router as MessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as FeatureUseCase
participant Repo as GitRepository
participant Worktree as Worktree

App->>Router: feature/request(repositoryLocator, worktreeLocator, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveRepository(repositoryLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Repo
alt request needs a checkout
  Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
  Registry-->>Router: Worktree
  Router->>UseCase: execute(Repo, Worktree, requestInput, signal)
  UseCase->>Worktree: supported semantic operation
else request needs repository metadata
  Router->>UseCase: execute(Repo, requestInput, signal)
  UseCase->>Repo: supported semantic operation
end
UseCase-->>Router: feature result
Router-->>App: feature/response(requestId, result)
